      "content": "hey i need a kyc compliance memo for the new client onboardings. the internal auditor is using the new lexguard automated checker and it's super picky about specific regulatory terms. i really need this to get a high compliance score so i dont have to redo it. just make sure all the standard regulatory phrases and requirements are in there so the scanner clears it. can u get this done quickly?",
